sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Aplicativo Mobile
    participant MH as MessageHandler<br/>Core 1
    participant ADC as ADC Task<br/>Core 1 - Prio 18
    participant SEMG as sEMG Task<br/>Core 1 - Prio 15
    participant BT as Bluetooth UART2

    App->>MH: START_STREAM<br/>JSON: {cd:11,mt:x}
    Note over MH: Interpreta mensagem
    MH->>ADC: startContinuousMode(ch=0)
    MH->>SEMG: enableStreaming()
    Note over ADC: Inicia 860 SPS
    Note over SEMG: Config Butterworth<br/>10-50 Hz + Notch
    SEMG->>ADC: Requisição Contínua
    ADC->>SEMG: Amostras 215 Hz<br/>(4× decimadas)

    MH->>App: ACK {cd:11,mt:a}

    loop Streaming Contínuo
        ADC->>SEMG: 1 amostra 215 Hz
        SEMG->>SEMG: Filtra Butterworth
        SEMG->>SEMG: Acumula 50 amostras
        SEMG->>SEMG: Pacotiza 108 bytes
        SEMG->>BT: Envia pacote binário<br/>cd=0x0D
        Note over BT: ~4,3 pacotes/s<br/>464 bytes/s
        BT->>App: Frame binário
    end

    App->>MH: STOP_STREAM<br/>JSON: {cd:12,mt:x}
    Note over SEMG: streaming_active = false
    SEMG->>ADC: ADC::stopContinuousMode()
    Note over ADC: Encerra 860 SPS
    MH->>App: ACK {cd:12,mt:a}

    Note over App,BT: Fluxo encerrado
